OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be cloudy and breezy
OL,6,Fthroughout the day as outbreaks of
OL,7,Frain move northeast, these heavy at
OL,8,Ftimes. Some drier and brighter spells
OL,9,Fdeveloping over western counties in
OL,10,Fthe afternoon.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FCloudy with occasionally
OL,13,Fheavy rain in the east at first.
OL,14,FDrier, clearer weather in the west
OL,15,Fwill spread to all through the
OL,16,Fevening. Mostly dry overnight, few
OL,17,Fshowers in northwest.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
