OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FDry and bright in the east in
OL,6,Fthe morning, a few showers in the
OL,7,Fwest. Bright or sunny spells and
OL,8,Fscattered showers everywhere in the
OL,9,Fafternoon, heavy at times.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FBright
OL,12,For sunny spells and scattered showers
OL,13,Fon Tuesday and Wednesday, heavy and
OL,14,Fthundery at times. Turning windier
OL,15,Fwith widespread cloud and rain
OL,16,Farriving from the west on Thursday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
